; New variety: a pair of fast, fragile Ash Swarmers rush in first (test flinch +
; knockback on light enemies); a Venom Spitter holds at range and fires its poison
; volley special; an armored Iron Bruiser plods in with its telegraphed slam; and the
; Magma Colossus mini-boss waits at the far end (test the wind-up tell + phase 2 at 50%).
