; Bullet-hell casters: the Cinder Caster holds at range and unleashes 360-degree RING
; barrages of slow magma orbs; the Frost Caster fires fast frost-bolt volleys plus a
; 3-shot spread on its normal attack. Parked wide so their patterns are easy to read.
